  https://github.com/pyodide/pyodide
- pypdf — BSD-3-Clause — https://github.com/py-pdf/pypdf
- fpdf2 — LGPL-3.0 — https://github.com/py-pdf/fpdf2
- openpyxl — MIT — https://foss.heptapod.net/openpyxl/openpyxl
- python-docx — MIT — https://github.com/python-openxml/python-docx
- python-pptx — MIT — https://github.com/scanny/python-pptx
- Pillow — MIT-CMU — https://github.com/python-pillow/Pillow
- pdf.js (pdfjs-dist) — Apache-2.0 — https://github.com/mozilla/pdf.js
- tesseract.js — Apache-2.0 — https://github.com/naptha/tesseract.js
